Using Drumroll to send midi to Hydrogen

There's a script in the tools directory that will connect drumroll to hydrogen. Here's the steps:

Run drumroll with --alsamidi and --nosound options

    drumroll --alsamidi --nosound

Start Hydrogen with alsa audio driver

    hydrogen -d alsa

Run aconnect to connect Drumroll midi output to hydrogen midi input

    aconnect "drumroll" "Hydrogen"
